These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-1::.
There are 2 different nationalities: canadian, nigerian
There are 2 different favourite colors: mauve, azure
There 2 different types of food: cherry, kale
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: november, september
1. the person who's birthday is in september is on the left or right of the person eating kale##3
2. the nigerian is in an even position##4
3. the person who likes azure is the canadian##1
4. the person who's birthday is in september is on the right of the person who's birthday is in november##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |
| Nationality      | canadian  | nigerian   |
| Color   | azure     | mauve   |
| Food         | kale | cherry |
| Birthday     | november | september    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-2::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: chess, cooking
City: liverpool, hamburg
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: vegafina, oliveros
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: salsa, gospel
1. the oliveros-smoker is in an odd position##4
2. the person traveling to liverpool is the fan of gospel##1
3. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the right of the person traveling to hamburg##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |
| Hobby          | chess     | cooking |
| City   | hamburg | liverpool  |
| Cigar           | oliveros         | vegafina     |
| Music-Genre     | salsa   | gospel    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-3::.
There are 2 different nationalities: russian, spanish
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: superhero, horror
City: paris, london
House: modern, art-deco
1. the art-deco house is on the left or right of the person watching horror movies##3
2. the person traveling to london is on the right of the person watching horror movies##1
3. the russian is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |       2       |
| Nationality    | spanish     | russian |
| Movie-Genre         | horror | superhero    |
| City         | paris         | london        |
| House   | modern         | art-deco    |

