3. the gothic-revival house is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |
| Job      | manager     | social-worker |
| Nationality          | pakistani   | spanish  |
| Pet         | snake | hamster     |
| House   | cape-cod  | gothic-revival         |

