.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-6::.
The people use 2 different means of transport: airplane, jet-ski
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: game, blend
City: london, berlin
There are 2 different favourite beverages: sprite, fanta
1. the person drinking fanta is in an even position##4
2. the blend-smoker is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person driving the jet-ski is the game-smoker##1
4. the person traveling to london is on the left of the blend-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |
| Transport           | jet-ski | airplane    |
| Cigar   | game       | blend |
| City           | london         | berlin    |
| Beverage         | sprite    | fanta   |

