The people have 2 different hobbies: baking, filmmaking
1. the person who's sport is volleyball is in an odd position##4
2. the person who's hobby is baking is on the left of the person playing scrabble##1
3. the fan of metal is on the left or right of the person who's sport is volleyball##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |
| Game      | canasta    | scrabble   |
| Sport          | volleyball     | ice-hockey |
| Music-Genre           | techno | metal     |
| Hobby   | baking       | filmmaking     |

